# DOCS
# https://evo-integracao-api.w12app.com.br/swagger/index.html

### ========== ACTIVITIES ==========
GET {{url_base}}/api/v1/activities
Authorization: Basic {{token}}

### ========== PARTNERSHIP ==========
GET {{url_base}}/api/v1/partnership
Authorization: Basic {{token}}

### ========== PROSPECTS ==========
GET {{url_base}}/api/v1/prospects
Authorization: Basic {{token}}

### ========== SERVICE ==========
GET {{url_base}}/api/v1/service
Authorization: Basic {{token}}

### ========== EMPLOYEES ==========
GET {{url_base}}/api/v2/employees
Authorization: Basic {{token}}

### ========== MEMBERS ==========
GET {{url_base}}/api/v2/members
Authorization: Basic {{token}}

### ========== SALES ==========
GET {{url_base}}/api/v2/sales
Authorization: Basic {{token}}

### ========== MEMBERSHIP (PAGINADO) ==========
GET {{url_base}}/api/v2/membership?take=50&skip=0
Authorization: Basic {{token}}

### ========== ESTRUTURA DE RESPOSTA ==========

